welcome_prompt: Welcome to the real estate search bot!
initial_prompt: Please describe in your own words what you would like to find?
facet_prompt: What facet would you like to refine by?
facet_value_prompt: What value for %s would you like to filter by?
not_understood_prompt: I did not understand what you said
unknown_item_prompt: That is not an item in the current results.
list_prompt: Here is what you have selected so far.
not_added_prompt: You have not added anything yet.
no_values_prompt: There are no values to filter by for %s.
filter_prompt: Enter a filter for %s like "no more than 4".
no_results_prompt: Your search found no results so I undid your last constraint.  You can refine again.
